 South]] side [[Havant & Waterlooville F.C.|Havant & Waterlooville]] on a two-month loan in November 2015.<ref>{{Cite news |title=Theo wings his way to Hawks |url=http://ebbsfleetunited.co.uk/theo-wings-his-way-to-hawks/ |publisher=Ebbsfleet United F.C. |date=10 November 2015 |accessdate=24 August 2016}}</ref> After numerous loan extensions to Lewis's spell with Havant & Waterlooville, his stay was made permanent in July 2016.<ref>{{Cite news |title=HAWKS Sign Theo Lewis |url=http://www.havantandwaterloovillefc.co.uk/articles/2016/07/08/hawks-sign-theo-lewis.html |publisher=Havant & Waterlooville F.C. |date=8 July 2016 |accessdate=24 August 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|match played 28 April 2018.<ref>{{Cite news |title=T. Lewis |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/theo-lewis/69399/ |publisher=Soccerway |accessdate=24 August 2016}}</ref>}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[FA Cup]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[Football League Cup|League Cup]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" valign=\"center\"|[[Cheltenham Town F.C.|Cheltenham Town]]\n|[[2008\u201309 Football League One|2008\u201309]]\n|[[Football League One|League One]]\n|2||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||2||0\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Football League Two|2009\u201310]]\n|[[Football League Two|League Two]]\n|15||0||1||1||0||0||0||0||16||1\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Football League Two|2010\u201311]]\n|League Two\n|21||0||0||0||0||0||1<ref group=lower-alpha name=FLT>Appearance(s) in [[Football League Trophy]]</ref>||0||22||0\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Football League Two|2011\u201312]]\n|League Two\n|1||0||0||0||0||0||2<ref group=lower-alpha name=FLT/>||0||3||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!39!!0!!1!!1!!0!!0!!3!!0!!43!!1\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\" valign=\"center\"|[[Gloucester City A.F.C.|Gloucester City]] (loan)\n|[[2011\u20